OL,3,CRestore Britain announces candidate
OL,4,Cfor Greater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FRestore Britain has announced its
OL,7,Fcandidate Marlon West for the Greater
OL,8,FManchester mayoral election.
OL,10,FThe election was triggered by Andy
OL,11,FBurnham's by-election win to become MP
OL,12,Ffor Makerfield, with rules stating the
OL,13,Fmayor cannot be a sitting MP.
OL,15,FWest is a former mental health nurse
OL,16,Fand became a vocal activist on the
OL,17,Fissue of child grooming gangs after
OL,18,Fhis teenage daughter, Scarlett was
OL,19,Ftrafficked by gangs in Rochdale and
OL,20,Facross Greater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
