FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782409716
OL,3,CRestore Britain announces candidate
OL,4,Cfor Greater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FWest criticised the former Labour
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Mayor, saying
OL,8,FBurnham allowed children to be abused
OL,9,Fon his watch.
OL,11,FHe said: "I have lived and worked in
OL,12,Fthis city for my entire life. I have
OL,13,Fseen what good public services look
OL,14,Flike and I have seen what happens when
OL,15,Finstitutions fail the people they are
OL,16,Fsupposed to protect.
OL,18,F"Andy Burnham ran those institutions
OL,19,Ffor a decade while children were being
OL,20,Fabused on his watch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782409716
OL,3,CRestore Britain announces candidate
OL,4,Cfor Greater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,F"Greater Manchester deserves a mayor
OL,7,Fwho understands this city, fights for
OL,8,Fits people, and is not afraid to hold
OL,9,Fpower to account. I am standing
OL,10,Fbecause this city deserves better and
OL,11,FI know exactly what that looks like."
OL,13,FWith West as mayor, Restore said it
OL,14,Fplans to attract business investment,
OL,15,Fcut wasteful spending, including
OL,16,Fwithin Greater Manchester's Combined
OL,17,FAuthority, protect greenfield, and
OL,18,Foverhaul the transport network.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
