OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782409716
OL,3,CRestore Britain announces candidate
OL,4,Cfor Greater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FLeader of Restore Britain, Rupert Lowe
OL,7,FMP, said West's history of fighting
OL,8,Ffor justice proves he has what it
OL,9,Ftakes.
OL,11,F"Marlon West spent years fighting for
OL,12,Fvictims that politicians like Andy
OL,13,FBurnham chose to ignore. He knows this
OL,14,Fcity and he knows its people. Greater
OL,15,FManchester deserves better leadership
OL,16,Fthan it has had.
OL,18,F"Marlon has already proved he fights
OL,19,Ffor this city when it matters. Now he
OL,20,Fwants to run it."
OL,26,@|D@QO]
