OL,3,CRestore Britain announces candidate
OL,4,Cfor Greater Manchester mayoral election
OL,6,FThe mayoral election will take place
OL,7,Fon 30 July and will involve about two
OL,8,Fmillion potential voters. The only
OL,9,Fother confirmed candidate is the Green
OL,10,FParty's Geraldine Coggins.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
